								<div class="bbWrapper">Hello Decimation's Staff . <br />
When i was playing on the server , I found a lot of bugs and glitch , so here it is :<br />
<br />
Bug of Decimation ( Program / Server ) :<br />
- When we do F3 with gun in the hand , we see the cursor on the middle of the screen.<br />
-People who use Decimation on MAC can't pick item on the ground.<br />
-When someone Combat Logged , he's corpse disapear .<br />
<br />
Problem maybe not bugs : <br />
-When someone prone , he take less damage than someone is up ( Maybe the hitbox has to be fixed ).<br />
<br />
<br />
Thank for have heard me , you dear butler , thyrdon .</div>
